# Configuration Files Guide

## TypeScript Configuration
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript compiler settings
  - Target: ES2024 with strict type checking
  - Output to [static/js/](mdc:static/js/) directory
  - Source maps enabled for debugging

## Package Management
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Frontend dependencies
  - TypeScript, Sass, jQuery, Showdown.js, Highlight.js
  - Development tools: TypeScript compiler, Sass compiler
- [Pipfile](mdc:Pipfile) - Python dependencies
  - Flask, OpenAI, Pydantic, Requests, Pillow, Wand
  - Development: pytest, ruff, prettier

## Code Quality
- [ruff.toml](mdc:ruff.toml) - Python linting configuration
  - Python 3.13 target
  - Enforce code style and best practices
- [.prettierrc](mdc:.prettierrc) - Code formatting rules
  - 4-space tabs, 120 character width
  - Consistent formatting across the project

## Test Configuration
- [pytest.ini](mdc:pytest.ini) - Test configuration
  - Environment variable loading
  - Test discovery and execution settings

## Environment Variables
- `.env.local` - API keys and configuration (gitignored)
  - `OPENAI_API_KEY`, `STABILITY_API_KEY`, `NOVELAI_API_KEY`
  - `FLASK_ENV`, `FLASK_DEBUG`, `SECRET_KEY`

## Build Scripts
- [run.ps1](mdc:run.ps1) - Development server startup
- [run-user.ps1](mdc:run-user.ps1) - User-specific development script
